@a128 7
.BI "Option \*qOverlay\*q \*q" value \*q
Enable 8+24 overlay mode.  Only appropriate for depth 24. 
Recognized values are: "8,24", "24,8". Default: off.
.RB ( Note:
the G100 is unaccelerated in the 8+24 overlay mode due to a missing
hardware feature.) 
